    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一名侦察船上的飞行员，被派往南河三星系，寻找恒星死亡的原因。飞行过程中发生了一些事情，您在冷冻舱中随着警报声醒来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403780/extras/92a718a06f35e1a24ebba1ced98ceb5d.poster.avif?t=1771231272\" width=1146 height=618 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403780/extras/92a718a06f35e1a24ebba1ced98ceb5d.webm?t=1771231272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403780/extras/92a718a06f35e1a24ebba1ced98ceb5d.mp4?t=1771231272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在未知且充满敌意的环境中努力生存，解开黑洞之谜，完成你的使命，最终找到返回地球的途径。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403780/extras/abb3b140f4bdfd8348aae68e6e885d78.poster.avif?t=1771231272\" width=1170 height=632 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403780/extras/abb3b140f4bdfd8348aae68e6e885d78.webm?t=1771231272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403780/extras/abb3b140f4bdfd8348aae68e6e885d78.mp4?t=1771231272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
